OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781686099
OL,3,CStarmer defends signing G7 tribute to
OL,4,CTrump despite condemning Iran war
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has defended signing
OL,7,Fa leaders' statement at the G7 summit
OL,8,Fpraising the US President Donald
OL,9,FTrump's actions on Iran.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV News' Robert Peston,
OL,12,Fthe prime minister said he signed the
OL,13,Fstatement because "the deal is a good
OL,14,Fthing" and an "opportunity for a new
OL,15,Fchapter" in the conflict in the Middle
OL,16,FEast.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781686099
OL,3,CStarmer defends signing G7 tribute to
OL,4,CTrump despite condemning Iran war
OL,6,FThe statement signed by the PM and
OL,7,Fother G7 leaders and published on
OL,8,FWednesday praises the president's
OL,9,F"strong leadership" over the latest
OL,10,FIran-US peace deal, and describes a
OL,11,F"historic opportunity" for peace in
OL,12,Fthe region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781686099
OL,3,CStarmer defends signing G7 tribute to
OL,4,CTrump despite condemning Iran war
OL,6,FBoth Starmer and members of his
OL,7,Fgovernment have been heavily critical
OL,8,Fof the war in Iran, which began after
OL,9,Fjoint attacks by the US and Israel in
OL,10,FFebruary, with the PM saying he was
OL,11,F"sick and tired" of seeing energy
OL,12,Fbills rise as a result of it, whilst
OL,13,Fother ministers described it as a
OL,14,F"mistake".
OL,16,FAs a result of the war and the closure
OL,17,Fof the Strait of Hormuz, a major
OL,18,Finternational shipping route,
OL,19,Fhousehold bills and oil prices have
OL,20,Fsharply risen.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781686099
OL,3,CStarmer defends signing G7 tribute to
OL,4,CTrump despite condemning Iran war
OL,6,FAsked when we might see the Strait
OL,7,Freopen for shipping to resume, the PM
OL,8,Ftold ITV News "as soon as we can,"
OL,9,Fhighlighting the need to ensure it was
OL,10,Fsafe to do so.
OL,12,F"We've been talking to insurers," said
OL,13,FStarmer. "They want the reassurance
OL,14,Fthat it's safe to go through, so we're
OL,15,Fworking and monitoring closely with
OL,16,Fthem."
OL,18,FPointing to high energy costs for UK
OL,19,Fconsumers, he said: "Anybody who's
OL,20,Fbeen to the petrol station lately will
OL,21,Fknow the impact this has had.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781686099
OL,3,CStarmer defends signing G7 tribute to
OL,4,CTrump despite condemning Iran war
OL,6,F"My job is, of course, to help deal
OL,7,Fwith a global conflict, but also to
OL,8,Fmake sure the impact is mitigated on
OL,9,Four economy back at home, which for
OL,10,Feverybody listening and watching, this
OL,11,Fwill be the thing they're most
OL,12,Fconcerned about."
OL,14,FLast week, the defence secretary John
OL,15,FHealey resigned over what he described
OL,16,Fas a lack of investment in the armed
OL,17,Fforces, ahead of the delayed and much-
OL,18,Fanticipated Defence Investment Plan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781686099
OL,3,CStarmer defends signing G7 tribute to
OL,4,CTrump despite condemning Iran war
OL,6,FAsked why, given rising global
OL,7,Ftensions, he had been unwilling to
OL,8,Ffund the reported extra #10 billion
OL,9,FHealey had said was necessary to keep
OL,10,Fthe UK safe, Starmer said the former
OL,11,Fdefence secretary was wrong.
OL,13,F"I just disagree," said Starmer.
OL,15,F"This is about the capability for the
OL,16,Ffuture... and it's not the last word
OL,17,Fbecause we have a commitment to 3%,"
OL,18,Fsaid the PM, pointing to the UK's
OL,19,Fcommitment to increase defence
OL,20,Fspending to 3% of GDP by 2030.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781686099
OL,3,CStarmer defends signing G7 tribute to
OL,4,CTrump despite condemning Iran war
OL,6,F"That is the assessment that I've
OL,7,Fmade, both of them hard-edged
OL,8,Fdecisions by the way, because the
OL,9,Fdefence investment plan involves
OL,10,Ftaking money from other government
OL,11,Fdepartments and reallocating it to
OL,12,Fdefence."
OL,14,FThe PM finished by saying he had made
OL,15,Fclear to the former defence secretary,
OL,16,Fas well as his successor, that defence
OL,17,Fis and always would be "a focus, and a
OL,18,Fpriority".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781686099
OL,3,CStarmer defends signing G7 tribute to
OL,4,CTrump despite condemning Iran war
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe question of the prime minister's
OL,12,Fleadership has continued to dog his
OL,13,Fpremiership, with an upcoming by-
OL,14,Felection in Makerfield on Thursday
OL,15,Fpotentially paving the way for the
OL,16,Fcurrent Mayor of Greater Manchester to
OL,17,Fchallenge Starmer for the keys to No
OL,18,F10.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781686099
OL,3,CStarmer defends signing G7 tribute to
OL,4,CTrump despite condemning Iran war
OL,6,FLast week ITV News conducted a focus
OL,7,Fgroup with voters in Makerfield, who
OL,8,Fall cited a deep dislike of the prime
OL,9,Fminister, in some cases more so than
OL,10,Fhis party.
OL,12,FPushed on this unpopularity, Starmer
OL,13,Fsaid: "We had an election two years
OL,14,Fago, which we won with a landslide
OL,15,Fvictory to change this country, and
OL,16,Fthat's what we're getting on and doing.
OL,18,F"I get up every day to work with the
OL,19,Fgovernment to improve the lives of
OL,20,Fmillions of people, that's why I came
OL,21,Finto politics."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781686099
OL,3,CStarmer defends signing G7 tribute to
OL,4,CTrump despite condemning Iran war
OL,6,FThe PM has continued to assert that he
OL,7,Fwill fight on as prime minister,
OL,8,Frunning in any leadership contest that
OL,9,Fmay be triggered.
OL,11,FPushed further on why he would not
OL,12,Fstand aside for someone more popular,
OL,13,FStarmer instead pivoted to his
OL,14,Felectoral mandate.
OL,16,F"We had a five-year mandate, we're
OL,17,Fonly two years into that mandate, but
OL,18,Fit's really important that we carry
OL,19,Fthrough the change that we were
OL,20,Felected into government to do.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781686099
OL,3,CStarmer defends signing G7 tribute to
OL,4,CTrump despite condemning Iran war
OL,6,F"I accept there's lots of talk in
OL,7,FWestminster. There always is. But I
OL,8,Fdidn't come into politics to get
OL,9,Finvolved in talking in Westminster. I
OL,10,Fcame in late in life in order to
OL,11,Fchange the lives of millions of people
OL,12,Fwho want and deserve, are entitled, to
OL,13,Fa better life.
OL,15,F"That's what gets me up in the
OL,16,Fmorning, that's what motivates me, and
OL,17,FI will never lose sight of that."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
